These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, cola, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, house, r&b
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
4 different games are played: chess, poker, domino, backgammon
 1. the person playing poker is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the fan of house##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 8. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage          | lemonade     | sprite   | coffee | cola |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | r&b   | house    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Game     | poker       | chess | backgammon  | domino      |

