.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, mystery
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, potato, asparagus, banana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, tennis, soccer
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
 3. the person eating banana is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 9. the person eating potato is the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | crime       | mystery | martial-arts |
| Food           | asparagus       | banana    | potato     | watermelon         |
| Sport     | soccer | tennis     | rowing     | snowboarding       |

