.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, pumpkin, radish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, daffodil, marigold
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | pumpkin      | plum   | apricot |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk | sprite | lemonade  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Flower           | daffodil      | balloon-flower          | marigold | daisy  |

