 4. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person traveling to nizza and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the musician is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
