 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
