 4. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person eating plum is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 8. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 9. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
