The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, hip-hop, salsa
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, old-henry, bluemaster
 1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the cottage house##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 3. the oliveros-smoker is between the person watching musical movies and the ranch-style house##2
 4. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 5. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 6. the fan of salsa is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the wooden house##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
12. the wooden house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
