.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, rat, lizard
There 4 different types of food: banana, lime, potato, radish
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, car, skateboard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person driving the trike is between the owner of the pony and the person driving the skateboard##2
 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
 9. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Pet      | lizard   | pony | hedgehog   | rat          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| Transport           | tram | car        | trike | skateboard |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

