.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
House: townhouse, modern, wooden, craftsman
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, mah-jongg, domino
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the modern house is between the wooden house and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 7. the wooden house is the person playing poker##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the townhouse house##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| House           | craftsman   | townhouse  | modern        | wooden |
| Game   | snooker     | domino     | mah-jongg      | poker   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

