.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, lizard, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, dancing, singing, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | guinea-pig | lizard | horse  |
| Hobby   | dancing    | singing   | reading  | gardening     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 